lipids of the liver in the mice injected with 2-ME. Although no differences were 
observed in the superoxide dismutase activities, malondialdehyde concentrations 
in the livers of the experimental mice were significantly increased. Autopsy 
data showed that Dunn-sarcomas associated with amyloidoses occurred more 
frequently in the untreated mice.

